              "text": "### Developers and Enterprise Architects\nEnsure cloud services they use are designed and developed with security in mind.\n\n### DevOps and SRE Teams\nEnsure security is introduced ealy on and that cloud environments remain secure post-production.\n\n### InfoSec Teams\nSecure systems and also benefit from being aware of security capabilities and architecture.",
